{"tid":732522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺左膠騎劫左清萊山洞被困事件？","createTime":"2018-07-07T03:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T05:17:49.000Z","uid":73883,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2700370d083cd5e3aa632880b533f4a8c5085bf7","tid":732522,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"由發現班人未死開始，講講下已經將佢地英雄化。我都希望佢地獲救，但絕對唔應該將班人捧做英雄。而家有個救援人員因佢地而死，佢地尤其個教練應該要付上責任，點解？<br />\n<br />\n1. 山洞口有告示話危險叫人唔好入，但佢地照入<br />\n<br />\n2. 無足夠裝備就入去探險<br />\n<br />\n3. 雨季入山洞遇上暴雨就仆街係基本常識<br />\n<br />\n4. 活外活動前唔睇/唔理天氣報告<br />\n<br />\n5. 入到山洞見咁難行都無視危險繼續入而唔係調頭走<br />\n<br />\n連國際足協都邀請班學生出嚟去睇世界盃，啲左膠個腦係咪裝撚左屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c3ca6ebd62d5f9a03fcb71ba41b0f55c53ff9b","tid":732522,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"被困學生嘅朋友仔都話佢地早知山洞危險，學校老師都有 warn 佢地唔好去。<br />\n<br />\nFriends of the stranded Thai soccer team claim boys ignored warnings<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/real-life/news-life/friends-of-the-stranded-thai-soccer-team-claim-boys-ignored-warnings/news-story/5b275c2b688ace1ea0affdcd2c0bdf75\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Flifestyle%2Freal-life%2Fnews-life%2Ffriends-of-the-stranded-thai-soccer-team-claim-boys-ignored-warnings%2Fnews-story%2F5b275c2b688ace1ea0affdcd2c0bdf75&d=bfsb2Z%2BflDqDUoBqCQS%2FZozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=dc817851\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/real-life/news-life/friends-of-the-stranded-thai-soccer-team-claim-boys-ignored-warnings/news-story/5b275c2b688a